（与动词简单过去时连用）以前
之前；安大略美术馆(Art Gallery of Ontario)；以前的

以前；过去；早先；从前；先前；往昔

1.en: A few years ago, a 75-pound stingray leapt out of the Atlantic Ocean at Vaca Key and slammed into a woman, killing her in the process.
1.cn: 前几年，在大西洋威卡礁，有一条75磅重的魟鱼越到船上，意外地致使一个妇女死亡。

2.en: It was one of my little sisters 'name, but she died one year ago, you look like her very much.
2.cn: 这是我一个小妹妹的名字，但是她在一年以前死了，你看起来长的很像她。

3.en: He said his management contacted Renault once "weeks ago and that is all" .
3.cn: 他说他的经纪人数周之前和雷诺联系过，并且仅此而已。

0.en: Will, high school was a long time ago.
0.cn: 高中是很久以前的事了。

1.en: And about an hour ago, we made an offer.
1.cn: 大约一小时以前，我们开出了我们的价码。

2.en: It was a long time ago. It was less than a year ago. I know. But so much has happened.
2.cn: 很久以前的事了。不到一年前。我知道，但中间发生很多事。

3.en: But Kip didn't even have to be Kip. We just, we handled that all wrong. It was a long time ago.
3.cn: 阿吉也不该受到这样的待遇，我们以前处理得很糟糕，况且那是很久以前的事情。

4.en: Years and years ago there were these people called the Maccabees.
4.cn: 很多年以前，有一群人，叫做玛加伯人。

5.en: Once upon the time, in olden days, a long time ago... Mummy Pig has been up there for a long time. I can hear snoring.
5.cn: 很久以前，在古代的时候，故事是在很久以前。猪妈妈已经在上面待了很久了。我好像听见打呼声了。

6.en: No, about a month ago, she gave her number to some guy in a bar.
6.cn: 不，一个月以前，她还把电话号码 留给一个在酒吧认识的男的。

7.en: See, a long time ago, there was this family. The Papá, he was a musician.
7.cn: 很久很久以前，有这样的一个家庭，爸爸是一个音乐家。

8.en: Long ago, our enemy, the Gorg, invited the Boov to a peace meeting.
8.cn: 很久以前，我们的敌军，格尔族，邀请波波族参加一个和平会谈。

9.en: Ah, wow! Look at all these kids. It wasn't that long ago I had kids around the house.
9.cn: 看看这些孩子，不久以前我的孩子也满屋子跑呢。

10.en: If you recall, I pointed out the Check Engine light to you several months ago.
10.cn: 你还记得么，几个月以前，我告诉过你引擎检修灯在闪。

11.en: This is something I long ago came to Peace with in my role as the beta male. Open.
11.cn: 很久以前，当我陷入爱河的时候我是可以打开的，快开。

12.en: That's quite a long time ago, Daddy pig. It's lucky I've kept myself so fit and strong.
12.cn: 那是很久以前的事了猪爸爸。真幸运我仍然那么健康和强壮。

13.en: No, remember I came here when I was a little piggy. But that's a long time ago, Daddy Pig. In the olden days. Thank you Peppa.
13.cn: 哈哈，不会的，记得吗，我还是个小猪的时候就来过这里了。但是这是很久以前的事情了，猪爸爸。以前的时候。谢谢你，佩奇。

14.en: Long ago, the consort Yao Niang was the favorite of Emperor Li Yu. She was a dancer, like you.
14.cn: 很久以前，窅娘是皇帝李煜最爱的妃子，她跟你一样善舞。

15.en: Beth, we're not who we were. What was inappropriate two months ago is appropriate now.
15.cn: 贝思，我们和以前不一样了，两个月前不合适的，现在就合适了。

16.en: Tonight we'll hear the story of Krispy Bear. A long time ago, this little bear was alive.
16.cn: 今晚我们讲脆脆熊的故事，很久很久以前 这只小熊还活着 。

17.en: Look, I know I should have told you this a long time ago but I am not Drake Remore, OK.
17.cn: 我知道，我很久以前就应该告诉你了，我并不是德瑞克雷莫瑞医生。

18.en: Yes. What I mean is thousands of years ago, predators survived through their aggressive hunting instincts.
18.cn: 可以，我是说几千年以前食肉动物捕猎的本能一直存在着。

19.en: Oh, my God. That's wild. Yeah, but it was, like, a million years ago, so it doesn't matter.
19.cn: 我的天，那也太放肆了。是，不过那是很久以前的事了没什么要紧的。
